      <div class="repair-card">
        <div class="repair-title">Beverly Hills · Samsung French Door</div>
        <h3>"Ice maker stopped completely — no ice for two weeks"</h3>
        <p>Samsung French Door ice makers have a known issue with the ice maker assembly freezing over in high-humidity conditions. The fix isn't just defrosting it — that buys maybe two weeks before it happens again. The root cause here was a faulty defrost heater in the ice maker compartment.</p>
        <div class="repair-detail">Replaced defrost heater assembly with OEM Samsung part, verified temperature differential, tested ice production before closing out. Ice making normally 30 minutes after repair.</div>
